Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.92,0:00:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个对立的世界有着完全不同的经历\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}two hostile worlds that suffered very different fates.
