Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.26,0:00:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿着地球和火星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Along with Earth and Mars,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.98,0:00:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水星和金星组成了近日太阳系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mercury and Venus make up our inner Solar System.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.92,0:00:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木星 土星 天王星 海王星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Jupiter, Saturn, Uranus and Neptune,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.84,0:00:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个比一个远离太阳\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}these planets farthest from the Sun
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.78,0:01:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是拥有着气态外表的远日行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}make up the gassiest outer worlds of the Solar System.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.99,0:01:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在40亿年里这些近日行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Over 4 billion years, the inner planets
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.50,0:01:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在太阳系内各种杂乱物质的碰撞与结合下形成了各自的固体结构\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}bound enough interstellar debris to become rock solid.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.92,0:01:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们研究行星\NWhy do we study planets? Why do we study…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.44,0:01:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么研究天文学\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}astronomy at all?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.59,0:01:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某天我们也许不得不离开地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We some day need to go beyond the planet Earth
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.61,0:01:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们想永远生存下去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}if we expect to survive as a species for a very long time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.64,0:01:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须了外面有些什么宇宙的性质是如何的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And we need to know what's out there and what the nature of the Universe is.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.26,0:01:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们研究世界上任何感兴趣的事物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We're studying worlds where things are exotic,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.49,0:01:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过基本的物理化学原理\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but the basic processes of physics and chemistry at work
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.91,0:01:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟地球上的完全一致\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are really the same we see here on Earth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.11,0:01:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水星金星两石质兄弟 远在数百万英里外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Millions of miles separate us from our rocky cousins,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.37,0:01:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过研究过水星和金星后得到了许多基本数据\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but a tour around Venus and Mercury reveals a common DNA.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.64,0:01:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能够观测他们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We can go to Mercury and Venus and really look at these
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.11,0:01:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究他们的各项数据\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as places, as worlds with their own histories,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.34,0:01:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并立即联想到地球的这些数据\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then contextualize our own planet's history.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.45,0:02:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体型上金星是太阳系中第6大行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Venus is the sixth largest planet in the Solar System.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.22,0:02:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离地球最近时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}At its closest,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.45,0:02:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约距离2600万英里[4200万千米]\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it is 26 million miles away from Earth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.79,0:02:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一金星年等于225地球天\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A year on Venus lasts 225 Earth days.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.92,0:02:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上150磅的物体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And if you weigh 150 lbs on Earth,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.96,0:02:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在金星上只有136磅重\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you'd weigh 136 on Venus.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.58,0:02:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古罗马人观察金星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Venus, when the ancient Romans looked up,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.84,0:02:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们被金星美丽的外表征服\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they were captivated by its commanding presence.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.75,0:02:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称之为维纳斯--爱与美的女神\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They named the planet after their serene goddess of love and beauty.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.68,0:02:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在空中显得如此美丽\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's such a beautiful presence in the sky,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.18,0:02:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易被观测到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it seems obvious the connexion there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.55,0:02:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金星长期以来被当作地球的姐妹星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Venus has long been considered our sister planet
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.71,0:02:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为相近的距离和相似的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because of its closeness in composition,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.19,0:02:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引力 密度与大小\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}gravity, density and size.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.12,0:03:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金星和地球在许多方面就像双胞胎\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Venus and Earth are almost twins in a lot of ways.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.59,0:03:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎差不多大小 金星只是略小于地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're almost the same size. Venus is slightly smaller than Earth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.75,0:03:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果地球像篮球这么大 金星就像足球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So if Earth was a regulation basket ball, Venus is a soccer ball,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.13,0:03:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只小一点点 金星是地球最近的同伴\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}slightly smaller. And Venus is the closest planet to Earth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.39,0:03:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以至于有人一直以为地球金星是一个双子星系统\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So for a long time it was thought of literally as a twin planet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.17,0:03:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长期以来科学家们认为这个伴星像地球一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}For ages, scientists thought this twin,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.19,0:03:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有深海\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}like Earth, was a planet covered with deep oceans,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.13,0:03:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大片雨林\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lush rainforests,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.12,0:03:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有悬崖以至于深信不疑\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and had a climate that would give credibility
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.14,0:03:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为金星上也有智慧生命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to the notion that intelligent life could exist there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.34,0:03:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空时代以前人们普遍认为金星类似地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Before the space age, people thought it might be very Earth-like on Venus.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.06,0:03:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们开始观测 探索金星 发现这些结果完全是谬论\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the paradox is, when we actually got to Venus and started exploring it,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.65,0:03:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现那里环境跟地球大不相同\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the conditions there are so different.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.98,0:03:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果证明金星与其说是地球好姐妹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It turned out Venus was less of an exotic sister to Earth
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.20,0:03:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说是个恶魔兄弟\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and more of an evil twin.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.98,0:03:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个行星基本数据十分相近\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So here we have two very similar planets in their sort of bulk properties,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.81,0:04:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却最终进化成两个完全不同的形态\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but they've evolved to such different states.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.68,0:04:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引出了一个关于行星演化的有趣问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And that creates an interesting problem in understanding planetary evolution.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.45,0:04:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些特定的反应\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A sort of controlled experiment,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.62,0:04:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生在两个行星上\Ntake these two similar planets and let them go for…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.90,0:04:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断演化数十亿年为什么造成了最后的巨大差异？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}4 billion years, and then why do they end up so different?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.23,0:04:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先一些基本的差别\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}First, some of the basic differences.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.43,0:04:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金星被陨星撞击\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Venus has been hit hard with meteors.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.54,0:04:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一些撞击非常强\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One so strong that
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.91,0:04:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些科学家认为这甚至导致了金星的反转\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}some scientists think it may have reversed the planet's rotation.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.43,0:04:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金星自转很慢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Venus has a very slow rotation.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.72,0:04:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们称其为逆向自转\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And it has what we call "retrograde rotation".
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.95,0:04:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为自转的方向不同于太阳系中所有其他行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So it spins backwards compared to the direction of spin of all the other planets.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.65,0:04:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于逆向自转太阳从西边升起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Because of this retrograde rotation, the Sun rises in the West
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.14,0:04:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在东边落下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and sets in the East.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.88,0:04:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且金星的一天很长\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the Venusian days are long ones.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.44,0:04:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天的间隔如此长 从一次日出到下一次日出\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The amount of time from one sunrise to the next
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.32,0:04:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约等于8个地球月[解说有误 应为4个地球月]\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is about 8 Earth months.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.30,0:05:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金星上漫长的一天\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the orbital pattern and long days
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.56,0:05:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是非常难以忍受\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are not what make Venus so intolerable.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.60,0:05:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部分原因是其恶劣的气候\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In part, it's the wicked climate.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.79,0:05:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面温度高达900华氏度[500摄氏度]\NWith a surface temperature of 900 ℉,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.29,0:05:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是太阳系中最恶劣的环境\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Venus is the hottest planet in the Solar System.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.08,0:05:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行者经过这里将立即倒下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Travellers there would have their trip cut short in no time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.26,0:05:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许几秒钟\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It would take a matter of seconds,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.42,0:05:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许一秒钟然后走向地狱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}maybe one second, before they were gone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.84,0:05:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折磨致死\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Roasted to death.
